data.description: Charming 3-Bedroom, 2-Bath Home with Pool  Welcome to your dream home! Nestled on a picturesque, tree-lined street, this beautiful residence boasts everything you've been searching for. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a refreshing pool, this property is your own private oasis.  Key Features:  Open Floor Plan: As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan that creates a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The seamless flow from the living area to the family/bonus room provides an ideal space for entertaining, relaxing, and making lasting memories with loved ones.  Outdoor Paradise: The backyard is a true paradise, featuring a covered patio that's perfect for al fresco dining, a sparkling pool for those sunny days, and a built-in BBQ for your outdoor culinary adventures. It's the ultimate space for enjoying the California lifestyle.  Ample Parking: The front of the house offers an extra-large driveway with a gate, ensuring plenty of space for parking. Plus, there's RV parking, making it convenient for those with outdoor vehicles or guests.  Security and Style: The wrought iron fence and gate in the front not only provide added security but also add a touch of elegance to the property, enhancing its curb appeal.  Convenient Location: You'll love the convenient location just seconds from Highway 76, which connects you to Interstate 5 and the stunning beaches of the area within minutes. Whether you're heading to work or spending a day at the beach, this home's location is perfect for all your needs.  Don't miss the opportunity to call this house your home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this beautiful property your own.
